long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Prospectly.AI plugin will operate on LinkedIn and will help LinkedIn users gather prospect contact details and other relevant information. 

When LinkedIn users visit any profile, Prospectly will gather profile information from LinkedIn and identify the profile's contact details. The user can save visited profile and can download all saved profiles with contact details.
